channel.title: @@@ RoflScape v6 client -------release------- @@@
channel.description:
Recently I havn't been very Active or coding very much, so I felt like making a seventh Client, which would be 5x better than my last ones. The Previous clients I have Made had alot of bugs and problems with them, but with this client, I have decreased the bugs to a minimum, if not, no bugs at all. This one is also a smaller file, and alot faster to run.
Once I have finished Configuring my Server for My V4 client, and added the finishing touches to it, I will release my Server to go with this client, which will Include ALL the Features of my last Version of the server, plus ALOT more.
General Features
[ul][li]This is a 377 Client.[/li] [li]I have added about 10 New GFX's.[/li] [li]I have added 30+ Items to it.[/li] [li]his one has the Cache in the folder, along with the models.[/li] [li]New GameFrame, which is Very very nice.[/li] [li]Working Log-Out door[/li] [li]It is an OPEN Client, which means it has all the Java files included in the download[/li] [li]FULL Prayer HeadIcons, plus the Wilderness Skull.[/li] [li]GS Spec GFX's (Credits to Mr Gangster for Armadyl spec).[/li][/ul]
New Items
[ul][li]Full Void knight added.[/li] [li]Void knight Helmets added.[/li] [li]full Saradomin Dragon hide armour.[/li] [li]Full Zamorak Dragon hide armour.[/li] [li]Full Guthix Dragon hide armour.[/li] [li]Full Mystic (The styled set)[/li] [li]All GodSwords, including the Saradomin Sword[/li][/ul]
There are alot more, I will list them later.
New GFX's
[ul][li]Armadyl GodSword Special attack GFX.[/li] [li]Saradomin GodSword Special attack GFX.[/li] [li]Bandos GodSword Special attack GFX.[/li] [li]I have added the Quest SkillCape Emote GFX to this Client.[/li] [li]I have used the Summoning Skillcape emote GFX.[/li][/ul]
Client Link is at the Bottom of this post (Which means you can look at the pictures on the way down ).
[shadow=red,left][u][b]PICTURES[/b][/u][/shadow] MAIN PAGE [IMG]http://i470.photobucket.com/albums/rr67/bombtwinz/main.png[/img] DDS SPECS ARE REAL [IMG]http://i470.photobucket.com/albums/rr67/bombtwinz/magic.png[/img] ALL PRAYER WORKS: [IMG]http://i470.photobucket.com/albums/rr67/bombtwinz/smite.png[/img] [IMG]http://i470.photobucket.com/albums/rr67/bombtwinz/retribution.png[/img]
link: http://uppit.com/XG30QI
CREDS :::: 80% MEH. 20% PUR3 PK FTW
